---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About WPCNA
metaDescription: Learn what WPCNA is, when it meets, and how to get in touch.
pageClass: page-about
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import resourceCard %}
<section class="page-hero page-hero--compact">
  <div class="container page-hero__content">
    <p class="eyebrow">About WPCNA</p>
    <h1>About WPCNA</h1>
    <p>{{ site.mission }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--flush-top">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <article class="about-copy">
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>We're a group of neighborhood associations working together to help people stay informed and connected across White Plains.</p>
      <p>This site keeps the basics in one place so you can quickly see what's happening, when it is, where it is, and where to click next.</p>

      <h2 id="meetings">Meetings</h2>
      <p>{{ site.meetingNote }}</p>
      <p>If you want to follow what WPCNA is talking about, the agendas archive is the best place to start.</p>
      <p><a class="text-link" href="https://wp-cna.org/agendas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">See agendas</a></p>

      <h2>Why neighborhoods matter</h2>
      <p>White Plains is one city, but it doesn't feel the same block to block. WPCNA tries to keep that neighborhood perspective in view.</p>
    </article>

    <div class="about-sidebar">
      <figure class="about-photo">
        <img src="{{ site.aboutImage | withPrefix }}" alt="{{ site.aboutImageAlt }}" loading="lazy">
      </figure>

      <aside class="detail-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
        <h2>{{ site.contactName }}</h2>
        <p>{{ site.name }}</p>
        <p>{{ site.location }}</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
        <a class="button button--block" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">Email us</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tint">
  <div class="container section__intro">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Useful Links</p>
      <h2>A few useful pages</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container resource-grid">
    {% for resource in resources %}
      {{ resourceCard(resource) }}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
